'''Kansa''' anaa se '''kokoram''' ye yadee bi  eka a yare hodo bi ho. Ema onipa honam akwa no.

Nsusanso a kokoran de ba ebi ne mogyatuo,asotee, ewa ekyere ene nsesae a eba agynam mu.

Enewma yi a a yeka nso betumi efiriri yare foforo.
<ref name="NCI2014"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.cancer.gov/cancertopics/cancerlibrary/what-is-cancer "Defining Cancer"]. </cite></ref>

Sigaret ema kokoram wuo 22% of cancer deaths.<ref name="WHO2014"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs297/en/ "Cancer  Fact sheet N°297"]. </cite></ref> Anot 10% no  aka no no nso firi kesee .<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.cancer.org/treatment/understandingyourdiagnosis/examsandtestdescriptions/testingbiopsyandcytologyspecimensforcancer/testing-biopsy-and-cytology-specimens-for-cancer-how-is-cancer-diagnosed "How is cancer diagnosed?"]</cite></ref>

Wobetumi abo woho ban efiri kokoram se wo anom sigaret . Afei nso wo taa tenetene wapom nso etumi yi wo fri kokoram mu.<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://seer.cancer.gov/statfacts/html/all.html "SEER Stat Fact Sheets: All Cancer Sites"]. </cite></ref>

